Author: lauryleah
Text: same happened to me with fruits. Idk why but lately I'm so scared of fruits like apples or pears because i feel like their so high in calorie for such little..  a few months ago i would literally binge on them because they felt so safe to me. how times have changed ðŸ˜µ

Author: sjsmiles
Text: It seems common that things cycle in and out of Safe Food territory. It's kinda sad when my enjoyment of something is dampened by calorie anxiety, but I try to think of it as a compromise...like, the almond butter and strawberries have good nutrition and the butter is tangential.    I hope you still sang. :)
